		<div class="story-heads">
		<h1>Jayne Anne Phillips, Xochitl Gonzalez, T. C. Boyle, and more: 20 new books out today!</h1>
			</div>
	</div>
										<div class="byline-date">
					<span class="byline"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/juliahass/"  title="Julia Hass">Julia Hass</a></span>
					<span class="hr"></span>
					<span class="date">April 21, 2026</span>
				</div>
						<div class="story-body">
								<p style="text-align: left;">A great week for nonfiction, our week&#8217;s bounty includes a memoir by Jayne Anne Phillips, a survey of American men by Jordan Ritter Conn, and a deep dive analysis into one of the world&#8217;s most dangerous mysteries, the billionaire Elon Musk. There&#8217;s a selection of great looking novels out as well: a new work by Xochitl Gonzalez, T. C. Boyle, Sophie Mackintosh, and more. Read on for the full list below!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">*</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264554" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/jayne-anne-phillips-small-town-girls-a-writers-memoir/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir.jpg" data-orig-size="993,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Jayne Anne Phillips, Small Town Girls- A Writer&amp;#8217;s Memoir" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-678x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264554" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-199x300.jpg" alt="Jayne Anne Phillips, Small Town Girls: A Writer's Memoir" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-678x1024.jpg 678w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-768x1160.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Jayne-Anne-Phillips-Small-Town-Girls-A-Writers-Memoir.jpg 993w" sizes="(max-width: 199px) 100vw, 199px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Jayne Anne Phillips, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9780593804933" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Small Town Girls: A Writer&#8217;s Memoir</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Knopf)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Jayne Anne Phillips writes prose that reads like plainspoken poetry, full of startling and vivid images that bring a vanished world back to life before our eyes.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>Tom Perrotta</p>
